    "title": "Senior Doctor - Aster DM Healthcare Capital India - Freshers Welcome",
    "description": "We at Aster DM Healthcare Capital India are looking for an experienced Senior Doctor based out of Bhubaneswar. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Aster DM Healthcare Capital India:\nAster DM Healthcare Capital India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Provide high-quality patient care and maintain patient records\n• Diagnose and treat medical conditions following established protocols\n• Coordinate with multidisciplinary teams for comprehensive patient management\n• Administer medications and treatments as prescribed\n• Ensure patient privacy and maintain confidentiality\n• Monitor patient progress and adjust treatment plans accordingly\n• Respond to medical emergencies and provide immediate care\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Health Informatics\n• Proficiency in Patient Care\n• Proficiency in Surgical Procedures\n• Proficiency in Clinical Documentation\n• Proficiency in Medical Ethics\n• Proficiency in Infection Control\n• Proficiency in NABH Standards\n• Proficiency in CPT Codes\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Bhubaneswar, Odisha, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Aster DM Healthcare Capital India!",
